snippet.textDisplay: It is always fun to read these dick riding comments from kids. To judge this as Vidal’s fight is elementary at best. No need to over extended, or point out what is not there. Truth is, anybody can hop in the ring and punch gloves, elbows, and arms; when you swing, you are likely to hit. Nevertheless, I would of not scored it any different. It was because of Vidal’s activity that the other dude hesitated to attack at all. If Vidal had not been swinging and hitting gloves, elbows, and arms, he would of lost 100%. Lots of errors on both sides, but I am sure with time both fighters will get better. Do no hate just because it is an accurate statement.
